## Generic-Agent Note

This skill applies to **any generic agent** — Claude, Cursor, or any other planning-capable agent. It is not specific to any product. All agents using the harness planning loop MUST follow this skill when harness instructs MCP tool calls. The rules in this skill apply regardless of which AI system is executing the planning loop.

---

## When This Skill Applies

This skill is MANDATORY when harness returns `nextAction` containing:
- `agent_call_mcp_retrieve_memory_by_chunks`
- `agent_call_mcp_merge_retrieval_results`
- `agent_call_mcp_build_memory_context_pack`

Do NOT call any other MCP tool. Do NOT call MCP at other times.

